  "text": "Finally, the third pathway includes MH with concomitant chorioretinal atrophy or underlying macular scar. Both progressive retinal thinning over the lesion and tangential traction promote the MH formation that may occur adjacent to the margins or within the lesion area [CITATION_1] .",
